739
00:31:11,580 --> 00:31:12,831
[typing]

740
00:31:16,251 --> 00:31:17,878
All right, match point.

741
00:31:17,961 --> 00:31:18,962
Oh, yes.

742
00:31:19,046 --> 00:31:20,047
[Dusty groans]

743
00:31:20,130 --> 00:31:21,507
I'm gonna get ya.

744
00:31:24,843 --> 00:31:26,428
- Oh! Oh!
- Oh!

745
00:31:26,512 --> 00:31:28,305
Still got it! Yes!

746
00:31:28,388 --> 00:31:30,849
Would've been easier to have won that
with a dink, you know?

747
00:31:30,933 --> 00:31:32,643
Oh, never gonna happen. [chuckles] No.

748
00:31:32,726 --> 00:31:34,269
Well, that was easily the best game

749
00:31:34,353 --> 00:31:37,523
against a woman three decades
older than you I've seen you play.

750
00:31:37,606 --> 00:31:38,815
Yeah, easily.

751
00:31:38,899 --> 00:31:42,819
- Yeah! Yes! [chuckles]
- [chuckles] You're so proud of yourself.

752
00:31:42,903 --> 00:31:44,571
Well, I haven't been
getting a lot of wins lately.

753
00:31:44,655 --> 00:31:46,698
- Sad. [chuckles]
- It feels good.

754
00:31:46,782 --> 00:31:48,492
No, I know. Me neither.

755
00:31:48,575 --> 00:31:51,578
- Take 'em where we can get 'em. Cheers.
- Oh, yeah. Hell, yeah.

756
00:31:51,662 --> 00:31:53,080
