How about this?
When I yell switch, just switch.

830
00:34:56,722 --> 00:34:58,140
Well, we wouldn't have to switch so much

831
00:34:58,223 --> 00:35:01,268
if your bitch ass
wasn't playing that patty-cake bullshit.

832
00:35:01,351 --> 00:35:04,188
- Oh, come on.
- Admit it, now that was fun!

833
00:35:04,271 --> 00:35:06,982
Candace, it was a blast!

