852
00:35:46,438 --> 00:35:48,524
You said something that I find upsetting

853
00:35:48,607 --> 00:35:50,609
because that's a real trigger for me.

854
00:35:50,692 --> 00:35:52,903
- It is?
- Yes! It's a thing.

855
00:35:52,986 --> 00:35:55,906
Country music fans
who live outside the south,

856
00:35:55,989 --> 00:35:57,991
they have a very hard time with this.

857
00:35:58,075 --> 00:36:01,286
They encounter a lot of prejudice
just like that,

858
00:36:01,370 --> 00:36:02,829
and it's a serious issue.

859
00:36:02,913 --> 00:36:04,790
This is the weirdest thing
I've ever heard in my entire life.

860
00:36:04,873 --> 00:36:06,291
Hey, give me your phone.

861
00:36:06,375 --> 00:36:07,668
Give me your phone right now.

862
