Hey, just wanted to let you know that
my wrist is feeling really great, Dad.

906
00:37:53,273 --> 00:37:55,317
Yeah, I saw the doc.
He said I'll be totally healed

907
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,818
for any big matches coming up.

908
00:37:56,902 --> 00:37:58,654
Not necessary. Neil's our guy.

909
00:37:58,737 --> 00:38:01,865
Right, because of the wrist,
but what I'm saying is I'm feeling good

910
00:38:01,949 --> 00:38:05,118
and I-I'm keeping it loose just in case
you wanted the… the best player.

911
00:38:05,202 --> 00:38:07,955
