918
00:38:21,593 --> 00:38:23,136
What an absolute idiot.

919
00:38:23,220 --> 00:38:26,431
As if he thinks a Band-Aid
is gonna stop a friggin' bullet

920
00:38:26,515 --> 00:38:28,642
