934
00:39:22,696 --> 00:39:24,698
[scatting]

935
00:39:32,414 --> 00:39:35,167
Yes! Yes!

936
00:39:36,877 --> 00:39:40,005
What are you doing on your phone?
Are you filming me?

937
00:39:40,881 --> 00:39:42,883
